00:01:46.912 --> 00:01:53.919
All we say in word and in deed, we give all to the glory of God. And it's pretty amazing watching.

00:01:53.920 --> 00:02:00.654
See if people start leaving; watch. Isn't that neat? I don't want to look at it.

