00:02:06.526 --> 00:02:13.079
You can say we still made a touchdown even if they try to call it back.

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:20.155
But you know what? It's all to the glory of God. It's neat to watch it as we grow.

00:02:20.156 --> 00:02:36.639
We are 400,000 away from what the Lord said our goal was: to set out for and to believe God for a million-man and woman prayer army. And you know, there's a lot there. Isn't it amazing?

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:54.799
Most people would say, 'Well, you know, that was an overnight success,'and I say no, that's taken a lot of cultivation, an acceleration of walking with Him.

00:02:54.800 --> 00:03:09.474
Let's go ahead and get to the news. Now, I'm a little bummed for what I saw in the spirit and what manifested today.

00:03:09.475 --> 00:03:22.361
I didn't release this publicly until right now: what I saw in the spirit about the woman FED. Now, I saw this woman right here.

