I never made her public—who I saw—but I told you all, 'I see a woman, and I'm praying over this woman.'I knew in the valley of decision that Trump was making this week that this was a major decision concerning whatever the Lord had us praying over, right?

00:03:44.155 --> 00:03:56.639
He said the decisions he will make this week, going into the third, will be the fork in the road.

00:03:56.640 --> 00:04:12.312
And I saw this woman right here. Do you see her? I didn't know that she was even able to run and be a part of the Fed, but this is the woman I saw.

00:04:12.313 --> 00:04:22.879
And Braden said, 'Daddy, this is who I believe Trump is looking at.'Now, she didn't make it.

