Is that a good thing or a bad thing? I don't know. I haven't got to pray it out enough.

00:04:30.319 --> 00:04:46.074
But in the valley of decision, he picked somebody that was very hawkish.

00:04:46.075 --> 00:05:07.721
He picked this man today. Do you see who he picked today? This guy. He picked him. And does it matter what I feel?

00:05:07.722 --> 00:05:15.918
I mean, I have my opinion of what I feel in my spirit, of what I'm praying over, and does the Senate approve it?

00:05:15.919 --> 00:05:20.132
Because they have to approve it now and the things go before the Senate.

00:05:20.133 --> 00:05:27.752
But in my spirit, I have been praying over this since October, very strongly.

00:05:27.753 --> 00:05:35.145
And the major valley—isn't it amazing the Lord would give us even this week?

00:05:35.146 --> 00:05:44.239
He said he'll make major decisions that will make or break his term concerning the next couple of weeks going into the third.

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:58.079
This is January 30th and 31st; the third is next week. And everything the Lord said—these are major decisions concerning Iran, concerning Israel.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:15.953
How will we handle Israel? How will he handle Gaza? How will he handle liberating the Iranian people from a regime that is tyrannical, that is killing young people like nothing?

00:06:15.954 --> 00:06:28.079
It's like I talked to Donné Clement and Patricia, and we were talking about it.

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:39.758
It's like a Holocaust for all the bodies and all the things that are not being exposed and shown for what they are doing to their people; it's like a genocide.

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:53.331
And we pray for the Iranian people. We do. I pray for the Christians, the underground church of Iran in Iran, and that we would see a major revival.

00:06:53.332 --> 00:06:59.076
Remember, the Lord has shown us so many times that He was bringing liberation; He was bringing a major revival.

00:06:59.077 --> 00:07:09.679
And as I was sitting and I was praying even early this morning, the Lord said, 'It takes faith to believe that, Brandon.

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:20.829
You grabbed onto a word that I gave you, and you embraced it.'Now, I don't look at anything that God says to me; I just believe it.

00:07:20.830 --> 00:07:26.443
I don't even realize it until He said it today when I was praying early this morning.

00:07:26.444 --> 00:07:42.225
He said, 'You grabbed onto it, and you're receiving it by faith and you don't even realize it.'I'm fully persuaded once He says something to me of that magnitude and I see it like that, I know that it's coming to pass.

00:07:42.226 --> 00:07:56.959
But there's no fruit of it yet. But whenever He spoke this to us—this is over a year ago—He said to us that we're bringing liberation and He's going to bring a major revival to Iran.

00:07:56.960 --> 00:08:11.002
And there would be things that are underground and archaeological discoveries in the days ahead that will come up out of the ground that will shake the Muslim community.

00:08:11.003 --> 00:08:23.355
So I just grab ahold of it and it's just like Abraham; I'm fully persuaded that what He has promised, He is able also to perform. When He said, 'You're going to have a million subscribers.

00:08:23.356 --> 00:08:54.998
I want you to have a million-man and woman prayer army.'Two years ago when we had a hundred subscribers or less—of course, everybody starts out with nothing other than the family members who were excited that you started a YouTube channel—and then they join on and say, 'Oh yeah, we're subscribed; we're watching, good luck'—and then you set out and you go, 'I'm going to do this.'And then look what happens—the Lord does it just like He said it.

00:08:54.999 --> 00:09:02.479
And I just receive it by faith. I receive it just like when He said, 'Brandon, Megan will be completely healed.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:19.274
I'm going to restore that little girl, and she's going to come on the platforms that I've provided for you and she's going to be a testimony to the whole world that I'm still a Healer.'Have I seen the full manifestation of that?

00:09:19.275 --> 00:09:35.751
No. But I see fruit. And whenever you see the first blossoms on the tree sometimes, then you may see the little bud with the little fruit on there, and you can see there's something there.

00:09:35.752 --> 00:09:39.155
But you're so far from tasting the full manifestation of it.

00:09:39.156 --> 00:09:45.304
All you have to do is just be patient and be giving God glory as you see the fruit ripen on the tree.

00:09:45.305 --> 00:09:56.158
It just takes time sometimes over the course of spring into summer to fall.

00:09:56.159 --> 00:10:04.699
Ripe apples come on the tree, and then in September, usually first of October, you get a really nice harvest of good apples.

00:10:04.700 --> 00:10:12.300
We had an old apple tree at our old house, and we used to get those apples and eat them. They were so good and so sweet, but it took forever.

00:10:12.301 --> 00:10:24.643
And Paisley, my little girl, would walk out there and say, 'Daddy, is it ready yet in July?'And I said, 'No, if you eat it right now, it'll give you a bellyache because it's not ripe.'But we knew if we'd just be patient and keep watching it.

00:10:24.644 --> 00:10:32.870
Even the little birds would come and lay there on the branches and peck at them a little bit at the top; they would get the firstfruits usually.

00:10:32.871 --> 00:10:43.560
But we knew that if we were patient, in due season—and a lot of you are in your due season—people may not understand what you're going through.

00:10:43.561 --> 00:10:58.437
They may look at you and say, 'He's cranky,''She's cranky,''He has all this going on because of the pressure.'It's the pressure that causes the coal to transform into that beautiful diamond.

00:10:58.438 --> 00:11:03.542
It takes pressure. And sometimes pressure makes you uncomfortable.

00:11:03.543 --> 00:11:09.039
The fruit in the process of waiting for something sometimes makes you uncomfortable.

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:21.531
But I'm trying to tell you, if you do not get weary in well-doing, do not get weary in well-doing, you will reap if you faint not.

00:11:21.532 --> 00:11:32.036
And I have seen it time and time again. If you are not weary in well-doing, you will reap the fruit of what you're believing for.

00:11:32.037 --> 00:11:44.398
If you just believe God and have that bulldog mentality and say, "God, I know I'm fully persuaded that what you have promised, you are able also to perform it.

00:11:44.399 --> 00:11:50.551
I am not letting go. I will not bow. I will not bend my knee to Baal.

00:11:50.552 --> 00:12:03.310
I will stand on the promises that you said that by your stripes Megan healed."And that's what you do and that's what you continue to do.

00:12:03.311 --> 00:12:13.359
And so if you have something in your life that seems to be impossible, God specializes in impossible situations.

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:22.730
All things are possible to him who believes. So, I want to encourage you tonight to don't give up on what you're believing for.

00:12:22.731 --> 00:12:29.437
There's an expiration date to your problems. There's an expiration date to what you're looking at.

00:12:29.438 --> 00:12:38.078
And say, "Hey, I'm telling you, in the name of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, be thou removed. Be thou cast into the sea.

00:12:38.079 --> 00:12:49.578
I will not doubt in my heart, and I know I will have whatsoever things I say."And I believe that this mountain is going to be removed in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:12:49.579 --> 00:12:56.390
And you just got to keep on keeping on. It's not one drop that makes the indention in those caves.

00:12:56.391 --> 00:13:12.078
It's thousands and millions of drops of water in that place consecutively that makes the indention inside of that rock.

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:24.159
And you look at stalagmites and stalactites or whatever they call them, and you see the tubes and you say, "Well, how long did that take?"Well, that took millions of years or hundreds of thousands or whatever.

00:13:24.160 --> 00:13:34.447
It's the faith that doesn't give up on the ground. It's the seed, it's the oak tree, it's the little acorn that doesn't give up on that ground.

00:13:34.448 --> 00:13:46.848
And it's even like Billy was saying today at his thing, you can pluck out the little seeds, but you can't go down and pick up an oak tree anymore because why?

00:13:46.849 --> 00:13:53.359
It's grabbed a hold of that dirt and it has a foundation. Its taproots went too deep.

00:13:53.360 --> 00:14:11.556
So when your taproot goes way too deep and you get your foundation and those roots down in that soil, no matter how bad the winds of life try to blow you over, you know that oak tree is going to make it through the storm, especially a healthy one.

00:14:11.557 --> 00:14:19.917
But a little acorn that just has barely any kind of root on it, a bird can pluck it up.

00:14:19.918 --> 00:14:27.537
But it's the faith of a mustard seed. You've got to have the faith of a mustard seed.

00:14:27.538 --> 00:14:31.599
It just takes a little bit to make that big old tree, that big old bush.

00:14:31.600 --> 00:14:36.687
It doesn't take a lot. Well, "Brandon, you've got great faith."No.

00:14:36.688 --> 00:14:43.759
Faith cometh by hearing and hearing by the word of God. How bad do you want your life circumstances to change?

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:50.920
The same pants I put on just like you, one leg at a time. And you've got to keep on keeping on.

00:14:50.921 --> 00:14:57.229
I even have my days. I get down, but I shake it off. I shake it off. I say, "I'm not going to get down anymore.

00:14:57.230 --> 00:15:03.011
I'm going to pick myself up out of this ditch."I pick Diana up out of the ditch.

00:15:03.012 --> 00:15:08.869
Braden picks us up out of the ditch. Paisley preaches to us and picks us up. We all know the ditch is there.

00:15:08.870 --> 00:15:15.119
Sometimes you fall into it, but you just pick yourself up, you brush yourself off, and you keep walking.

00:15:15.120 --> 00:15:28.293
When people try to knock you in the ditch, sometimes even family try to knock you in the ditch, you just say, "Hey, no, I'm not going to allow this phone call, I'm not going to allow this to derail me even from doing this video today."I have my obstacles.

00:15:28.294 --> 00:15:40.718
I have to keep myself strong. I am strong in the Lord and in the power of His might even whenever you wouldn't believe. And then people get so mad at me.

00:15:40.719 --> 00:15:48.319
They say, "Brandon, why do you talk about the haters?"You wouldn't believe the obstacles that I've come through this week.

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:52.564
You wouldn't believe it. And I refuse to talk about the problem.

00:15:52.565 --> 00:16:00.552
I've tried so hard to refrain from talking about the haters and talking about the YouTubers.

00:16:00.553 --> 00:16:05.079
But you know what? I know that persecution comes for the word's sake.

00:16:05.080 --> 00:16:29.278
And whenever it's accurate and people see that there's fruit behind you, when you're starting to go up the mountain and they are down here and they've been down here for years, they always try to attack the people that are on top because they say, "How did they get there?"But it was one rock at a time, the vision: "I'm going to get to the top.

00:16:29.279 --> 00:16:45.542
I'm going to be with you, Jesus. I want to be closer to you."One thing at a time, one day at a time, I choose to follow you. And I can't do this all on my own.

00:16:45.543 --> 00:16:59.313
It's like I was listening when Billy said today, Kathryn used to say all the time that God could use anybody other than her.

00:16:59.314 --> 00:17:03.789
God could have used all these people other than me. And that's exactly where I feel all the time.

00:17:03.790 --> 00:17:12.908
It's not Brandon Biggs. I am not able to see anything on my own.

00:17:12.909 --> 00:17:17.899
I'm not able to see in the future without Jesus. He shows me these things.

00:17:17.900 --> 00:17:22.300
I believe with all my heart because you can see it in the news a couple days later. Some people get mad.

00:17:22.301 --> 00:17:29.519
They say it's familiar spirits, but I know that it's Jesus because I feel His presence.

00:17:29.520 --> 00:17:39.678
And in His presence there's fullness of joy. In His presence there's fullness of peace.

00:17:39.679 --> 00:17:47.714
People may not understand your level that God's called you to, and they're not meant to.

00:17:47.715 --> 00:17:54.609
Usually, it's just those that are the closest ones, like Diana and my son and my daughter, and they understand.

00:17:54.610 --> 00:18:02.079
They've known the trial, they've known what we've been through, and they're the only ones that really matter.

00:18:02.080 --> 00:18:14.337
And sometimes it may just be that you're by yourself and you just keep walking through the mud and you'll get there.

00:18:14.338 --> 00:18:21.279
Keep on keeping on. Keep being obedient to the small things.

00:18:21.280 --> 00:18:27.331
It's not the great big things; that's the moment that happens every once in a while.

00:18:27.332 --> 00:18:34.798
It's the day-to-day, the mundane. What you do in the mundane will get you to the big event.

00:18:34.799 --> 00:18:40.399
But people want the big event, but they didn't get the day-to-day in the mundane.

00:18:40.400 --> 00:18:46.726
And I've learned this over the years. It's the janitor behind the toilet that cleans.

00:18:46.727 --> 00:19:02.558
And even I told the Lord if I had to go back to doing it again, that's where I found who I was. That's how I found who He was. It's the dying to self.

00:19:02.559 --> 00:19:12.719
And most people just want the aha moments, but they don't want to do what it takes to get to the process to get there.

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:27.599
And it's not easy. It costs a lot. And it's a lonely, lonely place because you don't let just everybody in your circle.

00:19:27.600 --> 00:19:37.678
It's a very lonely place. And I think that's a healthy place because He's in that place.

00:19:37.679 --> 00:19:46.879
It's not Kathryn. Billy always talks about how Kathryn was alone. She always talks about how she's alone.

00:19:46.880 --> 00:19:53.619
And I realize it is what she always says: "It cost me so much,"and I get it more and more all the time.

00:19:53.620 --> 00:19:59.279
This is what He said to me this morning in the wee hours of this morning.

00:19:59.280 --> 00:20:04.213
He said to me, because I said, "Lord, where's the greater percentage of the glory?

00:20:04.214 --> 00:20:18.719
What do we look for for healings and demonstration?"He said, "Brandon, what I'm calling for right now is the whole man."And He says, "You know a lot about deliverance because of what you've walked through.

00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:41.999
And I want not just physical healing, but in the soulish realm."And I will call people to walk in healings, demonstrations, manifestations, and deliverance ministry so that you will cast out devils in my name.

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:58.719
And he said, "I'm bringing a special anointing for casting out devils on certain individual ministries. I'm looking for the bride without spot or wrinkle.

00:20:58.720 --> 00:21:21.115
The spot and the wrinkle are sin and demonic oppression."And he said, "I'm looking for people to be completely free from the top of their head to the soles of their feet, Brandon."And there are so many people that have deviated off of deliverance ministry.

00:21:21.116 --> 00:21:31.960
It's gotten flaky over the years. And people have seen those who have grabbed onto it, they get flaky.

00:21:31.961 --> 00:21:37.750
I heard Billy talking about how people have buckets for vomit. Brother Hagin used to talk about this too.

00:21:37.751 --> 00:21:43.522
People had sacks and they'd bring them to church all the time because they were vomiting these devils up.

00:21:43.523 --> 00:21:52.798
Now, I have seen this happen. And it was through me when Jesus set me free.

00:21:52.799 --> 00:22:00.691
So, you don't throw the baby out with the bathwater. I have seen people get free and they throw up devils.

00:22:00.692 --> 00:22:07.988
Does it happen every time? No. So, you don't automatically carry some kind of bag around all the time.

00:22:07.989 --> 00:22:20.079
And how do you remain free? You'll know the truth, and the truth of God's word will set you free. It will set you free and make you free.

00:22:20.080 --> 00:22:28.048
Now, you have to have a foundation of the word of God in your heart to remain free after you get a critter out.

00:22:28.049 --> 00:22:41.678
Because of the things that I have walked through—and I've talked about this briefly, I don't talk about it a lot, it's my past—but I'm going to tell you, Jesus set me free.

00:22:41.679 --> 00:22:49.491
Jesus set me free. And I know what it's like to be bound by a lot of demonic spirits. And Jesus set me free.

00:22:49.492 --> 00:22:58.479
So the Lord talked to me about it this morning and he started talking to me about people getting free of demonic spirits.

00:22:58.480 --> 00:23:03.562
And I said, "What do I say to that?"He said, "Just tell it to come out. Don't entertain it.

00:23:03.563 --> 00:23:15.520
Tell it to come out."And he said, "I'll back you."I said, "Okay."He said, "I want the whole man: spirit, soul, and body.

00:23:15.521 --> 00:23:20.920
He wants you completely free in every area of your life."He wants you completely free of what you're bound by.

00:23:20.921 --> 00:23:36.486
Some people are bound by demonic spirits of addictions, alcohol, drugs, sexual perversions, anger, witchcraft, and all kinds of things like that that you've allowed the devil.

00:23:36.487 --> 00:23:45.519
When you open the door to the devil, the devil will come in like a flood.

00:23:45.520 --> 00:23:49.853
He's not a gentleman; he's going to take as much ground as he can as quickly as he can.

00:23:49.854 --> 00:23:58.836
And the moment he tries to get a hold of you, he'll try to get a stronghold on you. The Holy Spirit's a gentleman. He's always polite.

00:23:58.837 --> 00:24:07.248
He knocks on the door of your heart and asks, "Can I come in?"But he'll never force his way in.

00:24:07.249 --> 00:24:13.562
He's that still small voice on the inside of you. If you say, "Jesus, I want to make you Lord and Savior.

00:24:13.563 --> 00:24:20.745
I want to have a relationship with you,"it's a slow dance. It's not a microwave; it's a slow dance.

00:24:20.746 --> 00:24:25.842
It's an oven; it's a slow cooker. And everything is so polite with him.

00:24:25.843 --> 00:24:32.393
Now, the devil will run you ragged. Trust me, I've been there.

00:24:32.394 --> 00:24:36.552
And I don't give any place to the devil. I don't even like to talk about it.

00:24:36.553 --> 00:24:43.415
I don't talk about the occult or things like that very much. Why? Because they love pride.

00:24:43.416 --> 00:24:51.533
Satan was cast out because of pride, and pride likes to be talked about.

00:24:51.534 --> 00:24:56.432
We glorify God with our words and our expressions because he's worthy to be praised.

00:24:56.433 --> 00:25:01.618
We talk about him because it's the goodness of God that draws men to repentance.

00:25:01.619 --> 00:25:11.439
But most people, it's not pride. God is worthy and he is to be exalted above everything. He is amazing.

00:25:11.440 --> 00:25:21.735
But the devil's a loser and he lost, and Jesus made a display of him openly, triumphing over him in it.

00:25:21.736 --> 00:25:26.008
His defeat was made known throughout the whole angelic host.

00:25:26.009 --> 00:25:37.038
And they saw that Jesus Christ defeated him once and for all.

00:25:37.039 --> 00:25:49.038
And as he is, so are we in this world. Jesus Christ dwells on the inside of us.

00:25:49.039 --> 00:25:58.879
And so because he dwells on the inside of us, we have power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:11.918
I believe with all my heart, ladies and gentlemen, we are about to enter into the greatest revival this world has ever seen before because he's leaving the 99 to go after the one.

00:26:11.919 --> 00:26:20.662
He told me, "I'm coming to save that which is lost. I want the greatest harvest.

00:26:20.663 --> 00:26:27.804
Brandon, will you help me bring it in?"Just like Azusa Street, just like all these times. And that's what we're about to see.

00:26:27.805 --> 00:26:38.477
But not only are we going to see healings, we're going to see deliverances of demonic spirits that have oppressed and possessed people like the madmen of Gadara.

00:26:38.478 --> 00:26:46.046
