00:27:37.679 --> 00:27:46.399
Some people that are deaf and dumb don't realize it's a demonic spirit that is attached to their eardrum.

00:27:46.400 --> 00:27:58.377
They didn't disappear. Do you understand? The madmen of Gadara and the thousands of devils, the legions, they didn't disappear.

00:27:58.378 --> 00:28:04.158
They're still going through the dry places; they're still on this earth.

00:28:04.159 --> 00:28:15.519
I saw a girl at the grocery store and she started to manifest around us. I could smell it.

00:28:15.520 --> 00:28:22.751
The atmosphere changed and this demonic spirit tried to push against me to try to get me to leave because it didn't want me to witness to this young girl.

